caption.p:
The total content of four main active ingredients (baicalin, wogonoside, baicalein, and wogonin) in roots of 
   S. baicalensis under different treatments were estimated and analyzed. 
   D: drying; 
   S: steaming; 
   C: slicing. Different letters indicate significant differences of the total content of four main active ingredients among different treatments (
   P ≤  0.05). Data were presented as Mean ± SD.
